    {
      "type": "consequence",
      "character": "Mara",
      "text": "was still there an hour later. She didn't mention it in the morning.",
      "condition": "ep1_mara_stays"
    },
    {
      "type": "consequence",
      "character": "Mara",
      "text": "had gone inside. She trusted him to come in when he was ready.",
      "condition": "ep1_mara_goes_in"
    },
    {
      "type": "consequence",
      "character": "Julian",
      "text": "had not answered her. The question had already answered itself.",
      "condition": "ep1_p26_silent"
    },
    {
      "type": "internalThought",
      "content": "9:43pm. The light in the upstairs window went dark.",
      "mindOf": "Julian"
    },
    {
      "type": "internalThought",
      "content": "9:51pm. A shape moved past the window on the far end of the house. Fast. Low.",
      "mindOf": "Julian"
    },
    {
      "type": "internalThought",
      "content": "10:30pm. The shape didn't come back through the window.",
      "mindOf": "Julian"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Julian Crane",
      "content": "Someone went out."
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Mara Voss",
      "content": "What?"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Julian Crane",
      "content": "Upstairs. A shape past the window. Fast."
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Mara Voss",
      "content": "Julian, it's almost eleven. Somebody probably went to get water."
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Julian Crane",
      "content": "From the window."
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Mara Voss",
      "content": "They walked past the window."
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Julian Crane",
      "content": "They didn't come back through it."
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Mara Voss",
      "content": "Because they went back to bed through the door."
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Julian Crane",
      "content": "The light's been off since 9:43."
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Mara Voss",
      "content": "People sleep with the lights off. Julian. You need to stop."
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Julian Crane",
      "content": "You're right."
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Mara Voss",
      "content": "Come inside."
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Julian Crane",
      "content": "In a minute."
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Mara Voss",
      "content": "Now."
    },
    {
      "type": "internalThought",
      "content": "The window stayed dark. I went inside.",
      "mindOf": "Julian"
    },
